{
  "info": {
    "name": "KSeFFlow",
    "description": "KSeFFlow (e-invoicing) API \u2014 one folder per controller. Base path /api/v1 on port 8081. Auth is the httpOnly idToken cookie set by the RegulaOne backend: log in via RegulaOne SSO first (Postman cookie jar carries it), or paste a token into {{token}} for the Bearer fallback header.",
